descriptionHtml:
A Custom Player House.
- Number Of Chests To Place Your Items In, With Selected Chest Names.
- Located Inbetween Riverwood and Whiterun.
- Mannequins To Place Gear on !
- All Crafting Spots, Blacksmith, Alchemy, Enchanting, Workbench, Smelting, Tanning Rack, Cooking. - No DLC Required

NPCS Will Not Follow You Into the house, Creation Kit Didn't be Nice With Navmeshing
This is My First House Mod ;3


If You Have Any Problems Please Post Them In a Disussion And Ill Try To Fix As soon as I can.
-Same With Sugestions Let me Know !

Link To Steam Workshop, I Listed It There Too.
http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=250810176


Hope You Enjoy This House. The Key Is Located On a Barrel Near The Alchemy Table :)
author: Kariack
